IT was a historic home-coming for Jidenna recently as he visited Enugu exclusive to Urban Radio 94.5. The Nigerian-American had a whole day tour of his primary school, ESUT where he started a scholarship scheme for the best graduating student in computer engineering. His father was also a professor at ESUT. Jidenna Theodore Mobisson, known professionally as Jidenna, is a Nigerian-American recording artist signed to Wondaland Records. In 2015, Jidenna released two singles, “Classic Man” and “Yoga”, promoting the label’s compilation EP The Eephus.
